@madsmtm Are you aware of any issues like this? We're using `with_theme`, seems like that might have issues?

@sfsam If you're comfortable changing a couple lines of code, I'd be curious if this diff fixes it:

```diff
diff --git a/alacritty/src/display/window.rs b/alacritty/src/display/window.rs
index 09793fa0..341d0faa 100644
--- a/alacritty/src/display/window.rs
+++ b/alacritty/src/display/window.rs
@@ -173,6 +173,7 @@ impl Window {
             .with_fullscreen(config.window.fullscreen());
 
         let window = event_loop.create_window(window_attributes)?;
+        window.set_theme(config.window.theme());
 
         // Text cursor.
         let current_mouse_cursor = CursorIcon::Text;
```
